Kids say the Darnedest Things  will be on @CBS on May 5th y’all, my bad. I only said @ABC because that is where it was last year they canceled the show and @CBS picked it up.
Soooooo She Ready! But I just got nominated for a MTV Movie and TV Award for hosting Kids say the Darnedest things last year on ABC. We moved 
Soooooooooo 👀👀👀👀👀 watch @KidsSayCBS May 5th and go see @heretodaymovie in theaters May 7th you should  take your Mom it’s Mother’s Day weekend.😘

node.text: It’s time to take comedy back up a notch @laughfactoryhw. I want to do couture comedy shows where we get dressed up and put on a real show. What do you think @luxurylaw? I think about the times we are in and when people come out to see me they should get their whole money’s worth and they too should be able to dress up and feel beautiful if they want to. @christopherjohnrogers oh and @lizvig you can take my picture anytime #QueenoftheLaughFactory #CoutreComedy #highfashioncomedy #SHEREADY!

node.text: Last night I was very busy. In this Beautiful @christopherjohnrogers dress. 1st I went to the @laughfactoryhw and did a comedy show, then I went to a @sagaftra screening and Q&A of my New movie @thecardcounter that is in theaters now. Make sure you go see it this weekend if you ever cared about me. A special Thank you to the Glam team y’all stay making me pop.  Styled by: @luxurylaw  Makeup by: @ernestocasillas  Hair by: @hair4kicks  The Makeup in the Movie poster was done by the Great @makeupbydionne  and my nails for the movie was done by @lbc_lolo everyone I work with these days are Certified and over Qualified. Only the Best for Haddish these days. #SheReady #thecardcounter
